ngram\": \"the signs\", \"from\": 3106, \"to\": 3115}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Residents like Kevorkian and Hope have taken part in a city committee looking at ways to control the crowds and avoid a potential fire disaster.\", \"from\": 3129, \"to\": 3273, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Residents\", \"from\": 3129, \"to\": 3138}, {\"ngram\": \"Kevorkian\", \"from\": 3144, \"to\": 3153}, {\"ngram\": \"Hope\", \"from\": 3158, \"to\": 3162}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 3174, \"to\": 3178}, {\"ngram\": \"a city committee\", \"from\": 3182, \"to\": 3198}, {\"ngram\": \"ways\", \"from\": 3210, \"to\": 3214}, {\"ngram\": \"the crowds\", \"from\": 3226, \"to\": 3236}, {\"ngram\": \"a potential fire disaster\", \"from\": 3247, \"to\": 3272}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One idea being considered is providing shuttle service from Hollywood Boulevard to the Hollywood sign area, similar to the shuttle service which LA County provides to the Hollywood Bowl on busy summer nights.\", \"from\": 3275, \"to\": 3483, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3335, \"end\": 3354, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Boulevard\", \"score\": 0.9999999998981366, \"rank\": 1.0175832743820161e-10, \"text\": \"Hollywood Boulevard\", \"types\": [\"Q34442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Boulevard\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Boulevard\"}, {\"begin\": 3362, \"end\": 3376, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hollywood sign\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"One idea\", \"from\": 3275, \"to\": 3283}, {\"ngram\": \"shuttle service\", \"from\": 3314, \"to\": 3329}, {\"ngram\": \"the shuttle service\", \"from\": 3394, \"to\": 3413}, {\"ngram\": \"LA County\", \"from\": 3420, \"to\": 3429}, {\"ngram\": \"the Hollywood Bowl\", \"from\": 3442, \"to\": 3460}, {\"ngram\": \"busy summer nights\", \"from\": 3464, \"to\": 3482}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I would be in favor of a shuttle service.\", \"from\": 3485, \"to\": 3527, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"favor\", \"from\": 3500, \"to\": 3505}, {\"ngram\": \"a shuttle service\", \"from\": 3509, \"to\": 3526}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It makes sense.\", \"from\": 3528, \"to\": 3543, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"sense\", \"from\": 3537, \"to\": 3542}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You are bringing up less cars,\\\" said Zarrinnam of the Hollywood Sign Trust.\", \"from\": 3544, \"to\": 3619, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3598, \"end\": 3612, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hollywood Sign\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"less cars\", \"from\": 3564, \"to\": 3573}, {\"ngram\": \"Zarrinnam\", \"from\": 3581, \"to\": 3590}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Residents have also proposed making parking on the streets near the sign for 'residents only,' and they have gathered enough signatures for that.\", \"from\": 3621, \"to\": 3766, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Residents\", \"from\": 3621, \"to\": 3630}, {\"ngram\": \"parking\", \"from\": 3657, \"to\": 3664}, {\"ngram\": \"the streets\", \"from\": 3668, \"to\": 3679}, {\"ngram\": \"the sign\", \"from\": 3685, \"to\": 3693}, {\"ngram\": \"residents\", \"from\": 3699, \"to\": 3708}, {\"ngram\": \"enough signatures\", \"from\": 3739, \"to\": 3756}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They said they have yet to gain the full support of their City Councilmember Nithya Raman.\", \"from\": 3767, \"to\": 3857, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3844, \"end\": 3856, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nithya_Raman\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nithya Raman\", \"types\": [\"Q82